  <li id="comment-39189" class="comment odd alt thread-odd thread-alt depth-1">
    <header class="comment--meta">
      <div class="vcard"><cite class="comment-author fn"><a href="http://www.autoblowreviews.com" class="url" rel="ugc external nofollow">Vona</a></cite></div>
      <a href="https://orangette.net/2013/01/a-small-revolution/#comment-39189"><time class="comment-time" datetime="2013-05-11T13:15:27-04:00">Saturday, May 11, 2013 at 1:15 pm</time></a>    </header>

    
    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>I&#39;ve always tried to make those but always failed. *sigh* I guess I&#39;m gonna try again and see how it goes.</p>
<p>I had oat cakes in a shop once , and they were soooo yummy !!! Jeez everytime i try to replicate something i eat in a shop I end up making really disgusting food.</p>
